title: Hour 2 - Justin Fields Future, Tom Curran

description:
Dan wonders if Chicago Bears QB Justin Fields is worth re-signing to a long term contract. And New England Patriots insider Tom Curran breaks down the QB situation between Mac Jones and Bailey Zappe.
